[![DOI](https://zenodo.org/badge/304360097.svg)](https://zenodo.org/badge/latestdoi/304360097) Python tools with a GUI for visualization and analysis (target detection, PCA, material identification, library management) involving multispectral and hyperspectral images.  
  -To run with the GUI do "pip install HySpec" from the command line and then "import HySpec" from Python.  
  -There is a demo on YouTube at: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzUi-TW1M9mrxAZGKlCwsFzHDv4y3030B      ![](https://github.com/wbasener/HySpec/blob/main/spectralAdv/Screenshot_HySpec.png?raw=true)  
  NOTE: Dependency checking still in progress.

